* Define SVRCONN channel for client connections
DEFINE CHANNEL(DEV.APP.SVRCONN) CHLTYPE(SVRCONN) TRPTYPE(TCP) REPLACE

* Disable channel authentication for testing (simplifies setup)
ALTER QMGR CHLAUTH(DISABLED)
ALTER QMGR CONNAUTH('')

* Refresh security
REFRESH SECURITY TYPE(CONNAUTH)

* Display channel to verify
DISPLAY CHANNEL(DEV.APP.SVRCONN)
